title: Top 50 Best Piano Trance-Dance-Techno Songs of All Time
description:
Here are the 50 best piano trance songs ever created.  These go as far back as twenty years, and are as new as this month.  Songs were rated, found, and selected through an arduous selection proccess.  Best compilation of not only piano trance songs, but also trance songs in general, just check out the track list.  If you feel that I missed a song, that sucks, just leave a comment, and maybe I will make more editions.  If reception goes well, I will be making a second edition, as well as trance compilations of other instruments.  Enjoy!
